{"type": "article", "id": 18077, "title": "铅笔的设计", "description": "", "date": "2015-11-26T07:20:15Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 66, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702125733yxS8vGr52VkMswBQ.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t以色列霍隆理工学院大三的学生，在设计师 Luka Or 和 Keren Tomer 的带领下做了一组区别于传统的铅笔。带领人鼓励他们打破传统铅笔的形状，开发可能的新用途。最大的铅笔做成了一把刷子，刷开后有素描的效果，有的将笔杆做成了弯折的树枝，可以增加手感，最小的铅笔是两排牙齿，上下共八颗，在牙齿的中间夹着一个小的笔芯。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125730im9K7wBjAlYkvybg.jpg\" width=\"936\" height=\"1214\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.29700855\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021257312wUbiX4hatqx5IZE.jpg\" width=\"784\" height=\"560\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021257316bfNxBhIE3KJjRp1.jpg\" width=\"936\" height=\"629\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.67200855\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125732SuK0VxBnsqjHgYLo.jpg\" width=\"936\" height=\"624\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125732rPsJnxiQI4f0GRqe.jpg\" width=\"936\" height=\"624\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n"}